# Thesis Registry

<!-- 
This file stores structured thesis data. Each thesis has:
- id: unique identifier (THS-001, THS-002, etc.)
- title: thesis name
- status: draft | developing | mature | published | killed
- evidence: supporting data points
- counter_evidence: challenges to the thesis
- confidence: 0-100

Agents read from this file — never hardcode thesis data. 
The Synthesizer agent creates and updates theses.
